STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Damien JOHNSON, Defendant-Petitioner. State of New Jersey, Plaintiff,
v.
Brian Johnson, Defendant. C-981 September Term 2017
080712 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 22, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-716/1342-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
